      • merge

        public ResultIndex merge(ResultIndex other)
        Merge the given ResultIndex with this ResultIndex. If equal URI's are present the entry of this ResultIndex has precedence, unless the Result of the given ResultIndex has content. Invalidates the counter in this ResultMap: adding results or invalid URI-strings after this method not allowed.
        Parameters:
        other - ResultIndex to merge.
        Returns:
        this in merged state.
